OL,3,CManhunt after stabbing leaves man in
OL,4,C60s in critical condition on golf
OL,5,Ccourse
OL,7,FA manhunt is underway in Stafford
OL,8,Fafter a man in his 60s was found on a
OL,9,Fbench near the town centre in critical
OL,10,Fcondition after being stabbed.
OL,12,FStaffordshire Police were called at
OL,13,F7pm last night (May 15) to Newport
OL,14,FRoad, close to the Castle Golf and
OL,15,FLeisure, following reports of violence.
OL,17,FThe man in hospital had been walking
OL,18,Fon a public footpath through Stafford
OL,19,FCastle golf course when he was
OL,20,Fapproached by an unknown man and
OL,21,Fassaulted, according to police.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
