OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1779804667
OL,3,CManhunt after stabbing leaves man in
OL,4,C60s in critical condition on golf
OL,5,Ccourse
OL,7,FThey say he is in a critical, but
OL,8,Fstable condition.
OL,10,FOfficers say they were alarmed after a
OL,11,Fmember of the public found him on a
OL,12,Fnearby bench.
OL,14,FPolice officers were joined by West
OL,15,FMidlands Ambulance Service, the
OL,16,FMidlands Air Ambulance and the
OL,17,FNational Police Air Service.
OL,19,FDetectives are using drones and a
OL,20,Fhelicopter, and combing through CCTV
OL,21,Ffootage, to find the suspect.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
