CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1779804667
OL,3,CManhunt after stabbing leaves man in
OL,4,C60s in critical condition on golf
OL,5,Ccourse
OL,7,FPolice want to speak to anyone who saw
OL,8,Fanything suspicious in the
OL,9,FCastlefields area between 5 pm and 8
OL,10,Fpm yesterday.
OL,12,FChief Inspector Saqib Butt, our
OL,13,FStafford Borough local policing team
OL,14,Fcommander, said: "We understand this
OL,15,Fis a highly worrying time for our
OL,16,Fcommunities and we are doing all we
OL,17,Fcan to identify and apprehend the
OL,18,Fsuspect.
OL,26,@vD@ROU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
