CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1779804667
OL,3,CManhunt after stabbing leaves man in
OL,4,C60s in critical condition on golf
OL,5,Ccourse
OL,7,F"Anyone who witnessed anything
OL,8,Fsuspicious in the area before or after
OL,9,Fthe assault should contact us as soon
OL,10,Fas possible.
OL,12,F"We would like to thank everyone who
OL,13,Fhas provided information so far, and
OL,14,Fwe will continue our house-to-house
OL,15,Fenquiries today.
OL,17,F"We will be carrying out robust
OL,18,Fproactive patrols locally throughout
OL,19,Fthe day to help reassure residents
OL,20,Fthat we are there for them."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU|D@\O]
